subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities of national human rights institutions
subproject.description: This project seeks to enhance the communication and advocacy component of the GoP-UNDP Country Programme Action Plan (CPAP) through the documentation and production of knowledge management products on best practices and lessons learned of UNDP-supported programmes and projects in the areas of human development, democratic governance and conflict prevention and peace building; and the development of various information material (Annual Report, information kit, brochure) on UNDP-GoP Country Programme Action Plan (CPAP).
subproject.title: Knowledge Management
